(211, 41, 1, '', '2014-10-03 18:00:36', 303, 3767, '3c6d1167b37a1fc441a46147071cb06cd38befde', '{"id":41,"asset_id":"214","title":"Metr\\u00f4 vai funcionar no domingo das elei\\u00e7\\u00f5es","alias":"metro-vai-funcionar-no-domingo-das-eleicoes","introtext":"<h5 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">{loadposition position-10}<\\/h5>\\r\\n<h1 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px; text-align: justify;\\">Metr\\u00f4 vai funcionar no domingo das elei\\u00e7\\u00f5es<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p><em>Salvador, 02 de Outubro\\u00a0de 2014<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img class=\\"alignleft size-full wp-image-16596\\" style=\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sedur.ba.gov.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/10\\/1402597877120614CS_210e.jpg\\" alt=\\"1402597877120614CS_210e\\" width=\\"484\\" height=\\"317\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">Para facilitar o deslocamento dos eleitores para os locais de vota\\u00e7\\u00e3o, neste domingo (5), o metr\\u00f4 vai funcionar sem cobran\\u00e7a de tarifa, das 7h30 \\u00e0s 17h30, nas esta\\u00e7\\u00f5es Retiro, Acesso Norte, Brotas, Campo da P\\u00f3lvora e Lapa.<br \\/><br \\/>Mais informa\\u00e7\\u00f5es pela Central de Atendimento da CCR Metr\\u00f4 Bahia, no telefone 0800 071 80 20.<br \\/><br \\/>Como chegar \\u00e0s esta\\u00e7\\u00f5es:<br \\/><br \\/><strong>Lapa:<\\/strong><br \\/>Entrada pela Av. Vale do Toror\\u00f3, s\\/n, ao lado do Terminal de \\u00d4nibus Lapa;<br \\/><br \\/><strong>Campo da P\\u00f3lvora:<\\/strong><br \\/>Entrada pela Pra\\u00e7a do Largo Campo da P\\u00f3lvora, em Nazar\\u00e9;<br \\/><br \\/><strong>Brotas:<\\/strong><br \\/>Entrada pela Av. Mario Leal Ferreira (Bonoc\\u00f4) ou pela Rua das Pitangueiras \\u2013 Matatu de Brotas;<br \\/><br \\/><strong>Acesso Norte:<\\/strong> <br \\/>Entrada pela Rua dos Rodovi\\u00e1rios, s\\/n, antes de subir a ladeira do Cabula \\u00e0 direita, ou pela passarela do Shopping Bela Vista;<br \\/><br \\/><strong>Retiro:<\\/strong><br \\/>Entrada pela Rua Baixa de Santo Ant\\u00f4nio, Retiro.<br \\/><br \\/><strong>Fonte:<\\/strong> Secom<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">{loadposition position-4}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">{loadposition position-5}<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"40","created":"2014-10-03 00:14:39","created_by":"303","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2014-10-03 18:00:36","modified_by":"303","checked_out":"303","checked_out_time":"2014-10-03 17:58:16","publish_up":"2014-10-03 00:14:39","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":6,"ordering":"0","metakey":"","metadesc":"","access":"1","hits":"0","metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0),
(212, 42, 1, '', '2014-10-03 18:00:58', 303, 3269, '9109b41cb39b9daacfdd82cb3fb8614a3b6b33a0', '{"id":42,"asset_id":215,"title":"Trem do Sub\\u00farbio e Metr\\u00f4 funcionar\\u00e3o no domingo de elei\\u00e7\\u00f5es","alias":"trem-do-suburbio-e-metro-funcionarao-no-domingo-de-eleicoes","introtext":"<h5 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">{loadposition position-10}<\\/h5>\\r\\n<h1 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px; text-align: justify;\\">Trem do Sub\\u00farbio e Metr\\u00f4 funcionar\\u00e3o no domingo de elei\\u00e7\\u00f5es<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p><em>Salvador, 03 de Outubro\\u00a0de 2014<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>A Companhia de Transporte do Estado da Bahia (CTB) informa que o sistema de trens do Sub\\u00farbio de Salvador funcionar\\u00e1 no domingo, 05\\/10, dia das elei\\u00e7\\u00f5es, das 7h30 \\u00e0s 17h30.<br \\/><br \\/>As dez esta\\u00e7\\u00f5es (Cal\\u00e7ada, Santa Luzia, Lobato, Plataforma, Itacaranha, Escada, Praia Grande, Periperi, Coutos, Paripe) que comp\\u00f5em a linha Cal\\u00e7ada-Paripe estar\\u00e3o dispon\\u00edveis para uso pela popula\\u00e7\\u00e3o e os trens circular\\u00e3o com intervalo m\\u00e9dio de 40 minutos.<br \\/><br \\/>A passagem custa R$ 0,50 (inteira) e R$ 0,25 (meia).<br \\/><br \\/>Metr\\u00f4 \\u2013 Al\\u00e9m do trem do Sub\\u00farbio, o metr\\u00f4 da capital baiana tamb\\u00e9m funcionar\\u00e1 neste domingo. A Linha 1, em opera\\u00e7\\u00e3o assistida, vai funcionar sem cobran\\u00e7a de tarifa, das 7h30 \\u00e0s 17h30, nas esta\\u00e7\\u00f5es Retiro, Acesso Norte, Brotas, Campo da P\\u00f3lvora e Lapa.<br \\/><br \\/><strong>Fonte:<\\/strong> Ascom CTB<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">{loadposition position-4}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">{loadposition position-5}<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"40","created":"2014-10-03 18:00:58","created_by":"303","created_by_alias":"","modified":"","modified_by":null,"checked_out":null,"checked_out_time":null,"publish_up":"2014-10-03 18:00:58","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":1,"ordering":null,"metakey":"","metadesc":"","access":"1","hits":null,"metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0),
(213, 43, 1, '', '2014-10-03 18:03:45', 303, 4486, '523b0db9d065490d881c92829f6e51385a0f1cd0', '{"id":43,"asset_id":216,"title":"Metr\\u00f4 de Salvador ultrapassa o primeiro milh\\u00e3o de acessos","alias":"metro-de-salvador-ultrapassa-o-primeiro-milhao-de-acessos","introtext":"<h5 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">{loadposition position-10}<\\/h5>\\r\\n<h1 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px; text-align: justify;\\">Metr\\u00f4 de Salvador ultrapassa o primeiro milh\\u00e3o de acessos<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p><em>Salvador, 03 de Outubro\\u00a0de 2014<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Menos de quatro meses ap\\u00f3s o in\\u00edcio de seu funcionamento, o Metr\\u00f4 de Salvador registrou nesta semana o seu milion\\u00e9simo acesso. Segundo a Companhia de Transportes do Estado da Bahia (CTB), atualmente o Metr\\u00f4 transporta uma m\\u00e9dia de 18 mil passageiros por dia.<br \\/>O hor\\u00e1rio de funcionamento do metr\\u00f4, ainda em opera\\u00e7\\u00e3o assistida, \\u00e9 de 08h00 \\u00e0s 17h00, de segunda a sexta-feira, e das 8h \\u00e0s 13h aos s\\u00e1bados, em todas as cinco esta\\u00e7\\u00f5es da Linha 1 \\u2013 Lapa, Campo da P\\u00f3lvora, Brotas, Acesso Norte e Retiro.<br \\/><br \\/>\\u201c\\u00c9 gratificante, para todos que se empenharam, ver a popula\\u00e7\\u00e3o usando e cuidando bem do Metr\\u00f4. Temos v\\u00e1rios depoimentos de passageiros elogiosos \\u00e0 qualidade do servi\\u00e7o. N\\u00f3s estamos imbu\\u00eddos em melhorar cada vez mais e, eu tenho certeza, rapidamente outras marcas ser\\u00e3o alcan\\u00e7adas, principalmente a partir da opera\\u00e7\\u00e3o comercial e da inaugura\\u00e7\\u00e3o de novas esta\\u00e7\\u00f5es\\u201d, afirmou Eduardo Copello, presidente da CTB.<br \\/><br \\/>As obras do Metr\\u00f4 foram transferidas para o Governo da Bahia em maio de 2013 e, em junho de 2014, foi iniciada a opera\\u00e7\\u00e3o assistida do sistema, entre as esta\\u00e7\\u00f5es Lapa e Acesso Norte. Em agosto, a esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o Retiro foi entregue pela concession\\u00e1ria CCR Metr\\u00f4 Bahia.<br \\/><br \\/>Atualmente, quatro mil pessoas est\\u00e3o envolvidas na opera\\u00e7\\u00e3o e nas obras do Metr\\u00f4. A previs\\u00e3o \\u00e9 que a Linha 1 chegue a Piraj\\u00e1 em janeiro de 2015, totalizando 12 km, e que as obras da Linha 2 sejam iniciadas em novembro deste ano. At\\u00e9 o fim de outubro, o metr\\u00f4 continua em opera\\u00e7\\u00e3o assistida e as passagens permanecem gratuitas.<br \\/><br \\/>Elei\\u00e7\\u00e3o \\u2013 Dada a import\\u00e2ncia como meios de transporte e para facilitar o deslocamento dos eleitores soteropolitanos aos locais de vota\\u00e7\\u00e3o, o Metr\\u00f4 e o Trem do Sub\\u00farbio funcionar\\u00e3o excepcionalmente neste domingo, 5\\/10, dia das elei\\u00e7\\u00f5es, das 7h30 \\u00e0s 17h30.<br \\/><br \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Fonte:<\\/strong> Sedur<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">{loadposition position-4}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">{loadposition position-5}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"8","created":"2014-10-03 18:03:45","created_by":"303","created_by_alias":"","modified":"","modified_by":null,"checked_out":null,"checked_out_time":null,"publish_up":"2014-10-03 18:03:45","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":1,"ordering":null,"metakey":"","metadesc":"","access":"1","hits":null,"metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0),
