esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o Retiro foi entregue pela concession\\u00e1ria CCR Metr\\u00f4 Bahia.<br \\/><br \\/>Atualmente, quatro mil pessoas est\\u00e3o envolvidas na opera\\u00e7\\u00e3o e nas obras do Metr\\u00f4. A previs\\u00e3o \\u00e9 que a Linha 1 chegue a Piraj\\u00e1 em janeiro de 2015, totalizando 12 km, e que as obras da Linha 2 sejam iniciadas em novembro deste ano. At\\u00e9 o fim de outubro, o metr\\u00f4 continua em opera\\u00e7\\u00e3o assistida e as passagens permanecem gratuitas.<br \\/><br \\/>Elei\\u00e7\\u00e3o \\u2013 Dada a import\\u00e2ncia como meios de transporte e para facilitar o deslocamento dos eleitores soteropolitanos aos locais de vota\\u00e7\\u00e3o, o Metr\\u00f4 e o Trem do Sub\\u00farbio funcionar\\u00e3o excepcionalmente neste domingo, 5\\/10, dia das elei\\u00e7\\u00f5es, das 7h30 \\u00e0s 17h30.<br \\/><br \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Fonte:<\\/strong> Sedur<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">{loadposition position-4}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">{loadposition position-5}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"40","created":"2014-10-03 18:03:45","created_by":"303","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2014-10-03 18:05:20","modified_by":"303","checked_out":"303","checked_out_time":"2014-10-03 18:03:45","publish_up":"2014-10-03 18:03:45","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\