ed_by_alias":"","modified":"2014-10-31 02:10:07","modified_by":"303","checked_out":"303","checked_out_time":"2014-10-31 02:09:53","publish_up":"2014-10-17 23:28:50","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":8,"ordering":"1","metakey":"","metadesc":"","access":"1","hits":"9","metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0),
(248, 49, 1, '', '2014-11-03 17:50:46', 303, 4138, '6015a73848536af3550787b5b58be6bf0c4e0a67', '{"id":49,"asset_id":227,"title":"Metr\\u00f4 de Salvador atinge a marca de 1,5 milh\\u00e3o de passageiros transportados","alias":"metro-de-salvador-atinge-a-marca-de-1-5-milhao-de-passageiros-transportados","introtext":"<h5 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">{loadposition position-10}<\\/h5>\\r\\n<h1 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px; text-align: justify;\\">Metr\\u00f4 de Salvador atinge a marca de 1,5 milh\\u00e3o de passageiros transportados<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\"><em>Salvador, 3 de Novembro de 2014<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><em>\\u00a0<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><a style=\\"color: #0000cc; text-decoration: underline; line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sedur.ba.gov.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/08\\/1407791731110814CO_192_copy.jpg\\"><img class=\\"alignleft size-full wp-image-15218\\" style=\\"opacity: 1; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sedur.ba.gov.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/08\\/1407791731110814CO_192_copy.jpg\\" alt=\\"1407791731110814CO_192_copy\\" width=\\"441\\" height=\\"290\\" \\/><\\/a><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">Inaugurado no dia 11 de junho deste ano, o Metr\\u00f4 de Salvador alcan\\u00e7ou neste s\\u00e1bado (1) 1,5 milh\\u00e3o de embarques. A marca de um milh\\u00e3o foi alcan\\u00e7ada no m\\u00eas passado, segundo a Companhia de Transportes da Bahia (CTB).<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">O servi\\u00e7o opera de segunda \\u00e0 sexta-feira, das 8 \\u00e0s 18h, e de 8 \\u00e0s 13h, aos s\\u00e1bados. A Linha 1 tem 7,3 quil\\u00f4metros e liga a Lapa ao Retiro. A previs\\u00e3o \\u00e9 que a Linha 1 chegue a Piraj\\u00e1 no primeiro semestre de 2015, completando 12 quil\\u00f4metros iniciais de linha.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">A previs\\u00e3o \\u00e9 que todo o sistema metrovi\\u00e1rio fique pronto em 2017 com a entrega da Linha 2, que compreende o trecho entre o Acesso Norte e o Aeroporto Internacional de Salvador, passando pelo Detran, Rodovi\\u00e1ria, Pernambu\\u00e9s, Imbu\\u00ed, Centro Administrativo da Bahia (CAB), Pitua\\u00e7u, Tamburugy, Bairro da Paz, Flamboyant e Mussurunga.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><strong>Fonte: CCR Metr\\u00f4 Bahia<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">{loadposition position-4}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">{loadposition position-5}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"8","created":"2014-11-03 17:50:46","created_by":"303","created_by_alias":"","modified":"","modified_by":null,"checked_out":null,"checked_out_time":null,"publish_up":"2014-11-03 17:50:46","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":1,"ordering":null,"metakey":"","metadesc":"","access":"1","hits":null,"metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0),
