(271, 54, 1, '', '2014-12-04 18:13:51', 303, 7641, 'cc4cd14f2085f7b3c775eb862a77f4a219e5d794', '{"id":54,"asset_id":"232","title":"Metr\\u00f4: obras no trecho Retiro a Piraj\\u00e1 est\\u00e3o em ritmo acelerado, diz presidente da CTB ap\\u00f3s vistoria","alias":"metro-obras-no-trecho-retiro-a-piraja-estao-em-ritmo-acelerado-diz-presidente-da-ctb-apos-vistoria","introtext":"<h5 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">{loadposition position-10}<\\/h5>\\r\\n<h1 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px; text-align: justify;\\">Metr\\u00f4: obras no trecho Retiro a Piraj\\u00e1 est\\u00e3o em ritmo acelerado, diz presidente da CTB ap\\u00f3s vistoria<\\/h1>\\r\\n<h5 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\"><em>Salvador, 04 de Dezembro de 2014<\\/em><\\/h5>\\r\\n<p style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">O presidente da Companhia de Transporte do Estado da Bahia (CTB), Eduardo Copello, realizou na manh\\u00e3 desta quarta-feira, 03\\/12, uma visita \\u00e0s obras das esta\\u00e7\\u00f5es de Bom Ju\\u00e1 e Piraj\\u00e1, que fazem parte da Linha 1 do metr\\u00f4 de Salvador. \\u00cdtalo Roppa, vice-presidente do Grupo CCR, Harald Zwetkoff, diretor presidente da CCR Metr\\u00f4 Bahia, concession\\u00e1ria respons\\u00e1vel pelo Metr\\u00f4, Diretores da CTB e engenheiros da companhia tamb\\u00e9m estiveram presentes na vistoria, que serviu para avaliar o andamento das obras.<br \\/><br \\/>De acordo com Copello, a esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o de Bom Ju\\u00e1 tem 85% das obras j\\u00e1 executadas. \\u201cA via permanente e a estrutura da esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o est\\u00e3o prontas e em 20 de dezembro as obras civis da esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o estar\\u00e3o conclu\\u00eddas\\u201d, disse. O sistema de sinaliza\\u00e7\\u00e3o est\\u00e1 previsto para janeiro, quando poder\\u00e3o ser realizados os testes antes da opera\\u00e7\\u00e3o da esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o de Bom Ju\\u00e1. \\u201cNo piso superior teremos a plataforma de embarque, que est\\u00e1 90% conclu\\u00edda. J\\u00e1 no espa\\u00e7o inferior, as salas t\\u00e9cnicas, o acesso da esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o, os sanit\\u00e1rios, servi\\u00e7os de atendimento ao usu\\u00e1rio e a bilheteria\\u201d, explicou o presidente da CTB.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><img class=\\"alignleft size-large wp-image-18443\\" style=\\"opacity: 1; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sedur.ba.gov.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/12\\/Estutura-da-Esta%C3%A7%C3%A3o-Bom-Ju%C3%A1-em-constru%C3%A7%C3%A3o-Foto-de-Jefferson-Vieira-AscomSEDUR.jpg\\" alt=\\"Estutura da Esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o Bom Ju\\u00e1 em constru\\u00e7\\u00e3o - Foto de Jefferson Vieira AscomSEDUR\\" width=\\"495\\" height=\\"328\\" \\/><br \\/><br \\/>As obras da esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o Piraj\\u00e1 tamb\\u00e9m est\\u00e3o em acelerado andamento e, de acordo com Harald Zwetkoff, a previs\\u00e3o \\u00e9 de que a constru\\u00e7\\u00e3o seja conclu\\u00edda no primeiro semestre de 2015. A visita tamb\\u00e9m foi realizada no canteiro de obras onde est\\u00e1 sendo constru\\u00eddo o Parque de Manuten\\u00e7\\u00e3o de Trens, onde j\\u00e1 desponta a estrutura do futuro galp\\u00e3o. \\u201cNesse trajeto, ap\\u00f3s Bom Ju\\u00e1, a linha ser\\u00e1 bifurcada. Um trecho dar\\u00e1 acesso ao Parque, que servir\\u00e1 para armazenagem, manuten\\u00e7\\u00e3o e limpeza dos trens; o outro trecho seguir\\u00e1 para a esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o Piraj\\u00e1, posteriormente Campinas e \\u00c1guas Claras\\u201d, explicou o diretor presidente.<br \\/><br \\/><strong>Acessibilidade e seguran\\u00e7a<\\/strong> \\u2013 Dois elevadores, quatro escadas rolantes e piso t\\u00e1til s\\u00e3o recursos que est\\u00e3o no projeto da nova esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o de metr\\u00f4 no Bom Ju\\u00e1. Al\\u00e9m da estrutura de opera\\u00e7\\u00e3o dentro dos padr\\u00f5es de seguran\\u00e7a exigidos, a esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o tamb\\u00e9m atende a outros servi\\u00e7os que envolvem diretamente o passageiro, como acessibilidade e servi\\u00e7o de comunica\\u00e7\\u00e3o. Zwetkoff tamb\\u00e9m disse que o projeto ainda garante facilidade de acesso dos passageiros que utilizam outros meios de transporte.\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><img class=\\"alignleft size-large wp-image-18444\\" style=\\"opacity: 1; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sedur.ba.gov.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/12\\/Oper%C3%A1rio-trabalham-nas-obras-do-futuro-Parque-de-Manuten%C3%A7%C3%A3o-de-Trens-do-Metr%C3%B4-de-Salvador-Foto-de-Jefferson-Vieira-AscomSEDUR.jpg\\" alt=\\"Oper\\u00e1rio trabalham nas obras do futuro Parque de Manuten\\u00e7\\u00e3o de Trens do Metr\\u00f4 de Salvador - Foto de Jefferson Vieira AscomSEDUR\\" width=\\"455\\" height=\\"302\\" \\/><br \\/><br \\/><strong>Recorde<\\/strong> \\u2013 Nesta ter\\u00e7a-feira, 02\\/12, o Metr\\u00f4 de Salvador atingiu a marca de dois milh\\u00f5es de passageiros transportados desde o in\\u00edcio da opera\\u00e7\\u00e3o assistida, no m\\u00eas de junho deste ano. Desde que atingiu um milh\\u00e3o de usu\\u00e1rios, em outubro, o modal dobrou o fluxo de pessoas nos \\u00faltimos dois meses.<br \\/><br \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; background: transparent;\\"><em style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\\"><strong style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\\">Fonte: ASCOM CTB<br \\/><\\/strong><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; background: transparent;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">{loadposition position-4}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; background: transparent;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">{loadposition position-5}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"8","created":"2014-12-04 18:07:53","created_by":"303","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2014-12-04 18:13:51","modified_by":"303","checked_out":"303","checked_out_time":"2014-12-04 18:12:37","publish_up":"2014-12-04 18:07:53","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":3,"ordering":"0","metakey":"","metadesc":"","access":"1","hits":"0","metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0),
(272, 55, 1, '', '2014-12-05 15:31:45', 303, 4333, '4d850f67180b92ad9b174a8314a7165b7f5a438f', '{"id":55,"asset_id":233,"title":"RESULTADO DA PR\\u00c9 \\u2013 QUALIFICA\\u00c7\\u00c3O T\\u00c9CNICA RDC n\\u00ba 01\\/2014\\/CTB","alias":"resultado-da-pre-qualificacao-tecnica-rdc-n-01-2014-ctb","introtext":"<h5 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">{loadposition position-10}<\\/h5>\\r\\n<h1 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px; text-align: justify;\\">RESULTADO DA PR\\u00c9 \\u2013 QUALIFICA\\u00c7\\u00c3O T\\u00c9CNICA RDC n\\u00ba 01\\/2014\\/CTB<\\/h1>\\r\\n<h5 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px; text-align: justify;\\">Salvador, 05 de Dezembro\\u00a0de 2014\\u00a0<\\/h5>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">A Companhia de Transportes do Estado da Bahia \\u2013 CTB, por meio da Comiss\\u00e3o Especial de\\u00a0Licita\\u00e7\\u00e3o \\u2013 CEL, torna p\\u00fablico o resultado da pr\\u00e9-qualifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o destinada a identificar interessados\\u00a0em participar da futura licita\\u00e7\\u00e3o para contrata\\u00e7\\u00e3o integrada de servi\\u00e7o t\\u00e9cnico especializado de\\u00a0engenharia para a elabora\\u00e7\\u00e3o e o desenvolvimento dos projetos b\\u00e1sico, executivo e as built; a\\u00a0execu\\u00e7\\u00e3o das obras civis e de urbaniza\\u00e7\\u00e3o, fornecimento e implanta\\u00e7\\u00e3o dos sistemas fixos; o\\u00a0fornecimento e instala\\u00e7\\u00e3o dos sistemas de controle integrado de sinaliza\\u00e7\\u00e3o, tr\\u00e1fego, energia e\\u00a0telecomunica\\u00e7\\u00f5es; incluindo a realiza\\u00e7\\u00e3o de testes, a pr\\u00e9-opera\\u00e7\\u00e3o e todas as demais opera\\u00e7\\u00f5es\\u00a0necess\\u00e1rias e suficientes para entrega final do objeto, visando a implanta\\u00e7\\u00e3o de Ve\\u00edculo Leve\\u00a0sobre Trilho - VLT, no trecho Com\\u00e9rcio \\u2013 S\\u00e3o Lu\\u00eds, em Salvador-BA.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><strong>PRE-QUALIFICADOS:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Cons\\u00f3rcio Ferreira Guedes \\u2013 SETEPLA \\u2013 T\\u2019TRANS, Cons\\u00f3rcio VLT Salvador e Cons\\u00f3rcio TBHF\\u00a0VLT Salvador.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><strong>N\\u00c3O PR\\u00c9-QUALIFICADO:<\\/strong> Constru\\u00e7\\u00f5es e Comercio Camargo Correa S.A.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">Os\\u00a0Relat\\u00f3rios de An\\u00e1lises est\\u00e3o dispon\\u00edveis na se\\u00e7\\u00e3o <strong>licita\\u00e7\\u00f5es<\\/strong>, clique <a href=\\"index.php\\/licitacoes\\" target=\\"_blank\\">aqui<\\/a>\\u00a0para acessar<a href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.ctb.ba.gov.br.\\">.\\u00a0<\\/a><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">{loadposition position-4}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">{loadposition position-5}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"8","created":"2014-12-05 15:31:45","created_by":"303","created_by_alias":"","modified":"","modified_by":null,"checked_out":null,"checked_out_time":null,"publish_up":"2014-12-05 15:31:45","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":1,"ordering":null,"metakey":"","metadesc":"","access":"1","hits":null,"metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0),
