(276, 55, 1, '', '2014-12-11 15:42:28', 303, 4373, 'd44e28e7de28ee61b674bb50a6a0f17300fc32e8', '{"id":55,"asset_id":"233","title":"RESULTADO DA PR\\u00c9 \\u2013 QUALIFICA\\u00c7\\u00c3O T\\u00c9CNICA RDC n\\u00ba 01\\/2014\\/CTB","alias":"resultado-da-pre-qualificacao-tecnica-rdc-n-01-2014-ctb","introtext":"<h5 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">{loadposition position-10}<\\/h5>\\r\\n<h1 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px; text-align: justify;\\">RESULTADO DA PR\\u00c9 \\u2013 QUALIFICA\\u00c7\\u00c3O T\\u00c9CNICA RDC n\\u00ba 01\\/2014\\/CTB<\\/h1>\\r\\n<h5 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px; text-align: justify;\\">Salvador, 05 de Dezembro\\u00a0de 2014\\u00a0<\\/h5>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">A Companhia de Transportes do Estado da Bahia \\u2013 CTB, por meio da Comiss\\u00e3o Especial de\\u00a0Licita\\u00e7\\u00e3o \\u2013 CEL, torna p\\u00fablico o resultado da pr\\u00e9-qualifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o destinada a identificar interessados\\u00a0em participar da futura licita\\u00e7\\u00e3o para contrata\\u00e7\\u00e3o integrada de servi\\u00e7o t\\u00e9cnico especializado de\\u00a0engenharia para a elabora\\u00e7\\u00e3o e o desenvolvimento dos projetos b\\u00e1sico, executivo e as built; a\\u00a0execu\\u00e7\\u00e3o das obras civis e de urbaniza\\u00e7\\u00e3o, fornecimento e implanta\\u00e7\\u00e3o dos sistemas fixos; o\\u00a0fornecimento e instala\\u00e7\\u00e3o dos sistemas de controle integrado de sinaliza\\u00e7\\u00e3o, tr\\u00e1fego, energia e\\u00a0telecomunica\\u00e7\\u00f5es; incluindo a realiza\\u00e7\\u00e3o de testes, a pr\\u00e9-opera\\u00e7\\u00e3o e todas as demais opera\\u00e7\\u00f5es\\u00a0necess\\u00e1rias e suficientes para entrega final do objeto, visando a implanta\\u00e7\\u00e3o de Ve\\u00edculo Leve\\u00a0sobre Trilho - VLT, no trecho Com\\u00e9rcio \\u2013 S\\u00e3o Lu\\u00eds, em Salvador-BA.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><strong>PRE-QUALIFICADOS:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Cons\\u00f3rcio Ferreira Guedes \\u2013 SETEPLA \\u2013 T\\u2019TRANS, Cons\\u00f3rcio VLT Salvador e Cons\\u00f3rcio TBHF\\u00a0VLT Salvador.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><strong>N\\u00c3O PR\\u00c9-QUALIFICADO:<\\/strong> Constru\\u00e7\\u00f5es e Comercio Camargo Correa S.A.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">Os\\u00a0Relat\\u00f3rios de An\\u00e1lises est\\u00e3o dispon\\u00edveis na se\\u00e7\\u00e3o <strong>licita\\u00e7\\u00f5es<\\/strong>, clique <a href=\\"index.php\\/licitacoes\\" target=\\"_blank\\">aqui<\\/a>\\u00a0para acessar<a href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.ctb.ba.gov.br.\\">.\\u00a0<\\/a><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">{loadposition position-4}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">{loadposition position-5}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"40","created":"2014-12-05 15:31:45","created_by":"303","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2014-12-11 15:42:28","modified_by":"303","checked_out":"303","checked_out_time":"2014-12-11 15:42:15","publish_up":"2014-12-05 15:31:45","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":2,"ordering":"0","metakey":"","metadesc":"","access":"1","hits":"21","metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0),
(277, 56, 1, '', '2014-12-11 15:42:44', 303, 4463, '53828b5fd5461d1825af783df3dd0bcced3c891e', '{"id":56,"asset_id":"234","title":"Funcion\\u00e1rios do Trem do Sub\\u00farbio visitam instala\\u00e7\\u00f5es e conhecem opera\\u00e7\\u00e3o do Metr\\u00f4 de Salvador","alias":"funcionarios-do-trem-do-suburbio-visitam-instalacoes-e-conhecem-operacao-do-metro-de-salvador","introtext":"<h5 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">{loadposition position-10}<\\/h5>\\r\\n<h1 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px; text-align: justify;\\">Funcion\\u00e1rios do Trem do Sub\\u00farbio visitam instala\\u00e7\\u00f5es e conhecem opera\\u00e7\\u00e3o do Metr\\u00f4 de Salvador<\\/h1>\\r\\n<h5 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\"><em><i>Salvador, 11 de Dezembro de 2014<\\/i><\\/em><\\/h5>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img style=\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\" src=\\"images\\/materias\\/DSC_5474.JPG\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"509\\" \\/>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Na manh\\u00e3 desta quarta-feira, 10\\/12, os funcion\\u00e1rios da Companhia de Transportes da Bahia (CTB), que trabalham no sistema de trens do Sub\\u00farbio, tiveram a oportunidade de conhecer a opera\\u00e7\\u00e3o e funcionamento do Metr\\u00f4 de Salvador.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><br \\/>Eles foram guiados por colaboradores da CCR Metr\\u00f4 Bahia, concession\\u00e1ria que administra o sistema, e puderam conferir o moderno Centro de Controle Operacional (CCO), respons\\u00e1vel pelo monitoramento e funcionamento do sistema metrovi\\u00e1rio que j\\u00e1 transportou mais de 2 milh\\u00f5es de pessoas desde a inaugura\\u00e7\\u00e3o, em junho deste ano. Os funcion\\u00e1rios da CTB fizeram todo o trajeto atual da Linha 1 do metr\\u00f4 e puderam visitar as instala\\u00e7\\u00f5es em todas as esta\\u00e7\\u00f5es.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><br \\/>Segundo Dale Cristina da Silva, funcion\\u00e1ria da CTB que mora em Candeias e usou o metr\\u00f4 pela primeira vez, o servi\\u00e7o extrapolou suas expectativas. \\u201cEu n\\u00e3o imaginava que a estrutura era essa. Achei bastante interessante o funcionamento e espero poder voltar sempre, a partir de agora, e aproveitar ainda mais dessa estrutura\\u201d, afirmou.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; background: transparent;\\"><em style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\\"><strong style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\\">Fonte: ASCOM CTB<br \\/><\\/strong><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; background: transparent;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">{loadposition position-4}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">{loadposition position-5}<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"8","created":"2014-12-11 15:40:36","created_by":"303","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2014-12-11 15:42:44","modified_by":"303","checked_out":"0","checked_out_time":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","publish_up":"2014-12-11 15:40:36","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":2,"ordering":"0","metakey":"","metadesc":"","access":"1","hits":"0","metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0),
