(324, 67, 1, '', '2015-02-19 16:16:53', 303, 6571, '9179f9384d647a25bf68b66cb0b690638b84481c', '{"id":67,"asset_id":245,"title":"Metr\\u00f4 de Salvador transportou 150 mil foli\\u00f5es no Carnaval","alias":"metro-de-salvador-transportou-150-mil-folioes-no-carnaval","introtext":"<h5 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">{loadposition position-10}<\\/h5>\\r\\n<h1 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px; text-align: justify;\\">Metr\\u00f4 de Salvador transportou 150 mil foli\\u00f5es no Carnaval<\\/h1>\\r\\n<h5 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\"><em>Salvador, 19 de Fevereiro de 2015<\\/em><\\/h5>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 12.1599998474121px; line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">\\u00a0<a style=\\"font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; text-align: center; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #0066cc; background: transparent;\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sedur.ba.gov.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2015\\/02\\/DSC_8982.jpg\\"><img class=\\"size-full wp-image-19377\\" style=\\"border: none; margin: 5px 5px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%; height: 319px; opacity: 1; background: transparent;\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sedur.ba.gov.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2015\\/02\\/DSC_8982.jpg\\" alt=\\"Foto: Ascom Sedur\\" width=\\"482\\" height=\\"653\\" \\/><\\/a><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 12.1599998474121px; line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">Foto: Ascom Sedur<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 12.1599998474121px; line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; text-align: justify; background: transparent;\\"><a style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #0066cc; background: transparent;\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sedur.ba.gov.br\\/150-mil-folioes-passaram-pelo-metro-no-carnaval-2015\\/\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Durante os seis dias de Carnaval, o metr\\u00f4 transportou cerca de 150 mil foli\\u00f5es que curtiram os principais circuitos da festa na capital baiana.<\\/a>\\u00a0Funcionando das 5h \\u00e0 meia-noite, com acesso gratuito \\u00e0s esta\\u00e7\\u00f5es, o metr\\u00f4 fez cerca de 1.500 viagens. A esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o Lapa, a mais pr\\u00f3xima ao circuito Dod\\u00f4, no Campo Grande, foi a mais movimentada \\u2013 registrando 48.529 embarques, at\\u00e9 as 16h desta ter\\u00e7a-feira (17).<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; text-align: justify; background: transparent;\\">A atua\\u00e7\\u00e3o do Corpo de Seguran\\u00e7a da CCR Metr\\u00f4 Bahia, em a\\u00e7\\u00e3o conjunta estrat\\u00e9gica com a Pol\\u00edcia Militar, garantiram a seguran\\u00e7a e o bem-estar dos usu\\u00e1rios durante a opera\\u00e7\\u00e3o especial de Carnaval no metr\\u00f4.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; text-align: justify; background: transparent;\\">O primeiro ano de funcionamento do metr\\u00f4 de Salvador no carnaval encantou turistas e soteropolitanos com atra\\u00e7\\u00f5es musicais e atraiu a aten\\u00e7\\u00e3o dos foli\\u00f5es que aproveitaram o \\u00faltimo minuto para caprichar o visual na oficina de customiza\\u00e7\\u00e3o de abad\\u00e1s do metr\\u00f4 e com adere\\u00e7os de carnaval oferecidos pela concession\\u00e1ria.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; text-align: justify; background: transparent;\\">O sagu\\u00e3o da Esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o Lapa ganhou o som dos tambores das mulheres percussionistas da Banda Did\\u00e1, que empolgou os passageiros durante duas horas, no domingo de Carnaval. Na segunda-feira, foi a vez do branco e azul dos Filhos de Gandhy, com seus atabaques, agog\\u00f4s e xequer\\u00eas, darem as boas-vindas aos passageiros. No \\u00faltimo dia de atra\\u00e7\\u00f5es no metr\\u00f4, na ter\\u00e7a-feira, a banda Mal\\u00ea DeBal\\u00ea levou alegria e ritmo para dentro da Esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o Lapa com sua dan\\u00e7a. \\u201cO opera\\u00e7\\u00e3o do metr\\u00f4 no Carnaval cumpriu com um dos objetivos da concession\\u00e1ria \\u2013 aproximar o metr\\u00f4 da sociedade soteropolitana\\u201d, afirmou o Gestor de Atendimento da CCR Metr\\u00f4 Bahia, Hamilton Trindade.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 12.1599998474121px; line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\"><em><strong>Fonte: Secom Bahia<\\/strong><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: left;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 12.1599998474121px; line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">{loadposition position-4}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 12.1599998474121px; line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">{loadposition position-5}<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"8","created":"2015-02-19 16:16:53","created_by":"303","created_by_alias":"","modified":"","modified_by":null,"checked_out":null,"checked_out_time":null,"publish_up":"2015-02-19 16:16:53","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":1,"ordering":null,"metakey":"","metadesc":"","access":"1","hits":null,"metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0),
