(344, 71, 1, '', '2015-03-16 15:26:00', 303, 5599, '490de60ebb97bbd3c1ec84e6cf97b3fb6c4373da', '{"id":71,"asset_id":"249","title":"Secret\\u00e1rio refor\\u00e7a compromisso de transpar\\u00eancia com Minist\\u00e9rio P\\u00fablico","alias":"secretario-reforca-compromisso-de-transparencia-com-ministerio-publico","introtext":"<h5 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">{loadposition position-10}<\\/h5>\\r\\n<h1 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px; text-align: justify;\\">Secret\\u00e1rio refor\\u00e7a compromisso de transpar\\u00eancia com Minist\\u00e9rio P\\u00fablico<\\/h1>\\r\\n<h5 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\"><em>Salvador, 16 de Mar\\u00e7o de 2015<\\/em><\\/h5>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<h2>\\u00a0<\\/h2>\\r\\n<div id=\\"attachment_19563\\" class=\\"wp-caption aligncenter\\" style=\\"width: 586px;\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sedur.ba.gov.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2015\\/03\\/editada.jpg\\"><img class=\\" wp-image-19563 \\" style=\\"opacity: 1;\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sedur.ba.gov.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2015\\/03\\/editada.jpg\\" alt=\\"O secret\\u00e1rio Carlos Martins recebe a promotora Rita Tourinho na Sedur. Participaram do encontro o promotor Adriano Assis, o presidente da CTB, Eduardo Copello, e o chefe de gabinete da Sedur, Pedro D\\u00f3rea. Foto: Ascom Sedur\\" width=\\"458\\" height=\\"263\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n<h5 class=\\"wp-caption-text\\">O secret\\u00e1rio Carlos Martins recebe a promotora Rita Tourinho na Sedur. Participaram do<\\/h5>\\r\\n<h5 class=\\"wp-caption-text\\">encontro o promotor Adriano Assis, o presidente da CTB, Eduardo Copello, e o chefe de<\\/h5>\\r\\n<h5 class=\\"wp-caption-text\\">gabinete da Sedur, Pedro D\\u00f3rea. Foto: Ascom Sedur<\\/h5>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">A promotora Rita Tourinho, integrante do Grupo de Atua\\u00e7\\u00e3o Especial de Defesa do Patrim\\u00f4nio P\\u00fablico e da Moralidade Administrativa (Gepam), se reuniu na manh\\u00e3 desta sexta-feira, 13, com o secret\\u00e1rio Carlos Martins, na sede da Sedur. Na pauta do encontro foram debatidas as principais a\\u00e7\\u00f5es da secretaria, sobretudo nas \\u00e1reas de mobilidade e habita\\u00e7\\u00e3o.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">Durante a reuni\\u00e3o, a promotora apontou as principais demandas do MP na \\u00e1rea e ouviu do secret\\u00e1rio o compromisso de estabelecer uma rela\\u00e7\\u00e3o de transpar\\u00eancia em todas as obras lotadas na pasta. A visita teve como objetivo principal estreitar os la\\u00e7os com \\u00f3rg\\u00e3o, refor\\u00e7ando o conceito de dialogo com todas as institui\\u00e7\\u00f5es.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><strong>Portal<\\/strong> \\u2013 Est\\u00e1 em fase de desenvolvimento na Sedur, a cria\\u00e7\\u00e3o do Portal da Transpar\\u00eancia, uma p\\u00e1gina que vai reunir todas as informa\\u00e7\\u00f5es relativas as obras em andamento no estado. Dados como investimento, andamento dos trabalhos, montante investido, dentro outros, estar\\u00e3o dispon\\u00edveis para consulta popular.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">Os dados ser\\u00e3o atualizados automaticamente seguindo ritmo de andamento das obras. \\u201cEstabelecer uma rela\\u00e7\\u00e3o de transpar\\u00eancia com a sociedade civil \\u00e9 um dos princ\\u00edpios que vai nortear as a\\u00e7\\u00f5es da secretaria. A inten\\u00e7\\u00e3o \\u00e9 que as informa\\u00e7\\u00f5es estejam completamente dispon\\u00edveis para consulta p\\u00fablica\\u201d, explica Martins.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">Participaram do encontro o promotor Adriano Assis, o presidente da CTB, Eduardo Copello, e o chefe de gabinete da Sedur, Pedro D\\u00f3rea.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><em><strong>Fonte: Ascom Sedur<\\/strong><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 12.1599998474121px; line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">{loadposition position-4}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 12.1599998474121px; line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">{loadposition position-5}<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"8","created":"2015-03-16 15:20:03","created_by":"303","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2015-03-16 15:26:00","modified_by":"303","checked_out":"303","checked_out_time":"2015-03-16 15:25:27","publish_up":"2015-03-16 15:20:03","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":6,"ordering":"0","metakey":"","metadesc":"","access":"1","hits":"0","metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0);
