(365, 74, 1, '', '2015-03-26 20:20:15', 303, 2881, '4cc1cf05a188c7f5aaf2eced958d79e992bcd8dc', '{"id":74,"asset_id":"252","title":"Metr\\u00f4 n\\u00e3o funciona nos pr\\u00f3ximos s\\u00e1bados 21 e 28 de mar\\u00e7o.","alias":"metro-nao-funciona-nos-proximos-sabados-21-e-28-de-marco","introtext":"<h5 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">{loadposition position-10}<\\/h5>\\r\\n<h1 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px; text-align: justify;\\">Metr\\u00f4 n\\u00e3o funciona nos pr\\u00f3ximos s\\u00e1bados 21 e 28 de mar\\u00e7o.<\\/h1>\\r\\n<h5 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\"><em>Salvador, 20 de Mar\\u00e7o de 2015<\\/em><\\/h5>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">A CCR Metr\\u00f4 Bahia informa que, devido \\u00e0s obras de liga\\u00e7\\u00e3o entre a Linha 1 e Linha 2 do metr\\u00f4, todas as esta\\u00e7\\u00f5es estar\\u00e3o fechadas nos s\\u00e1bados 21 e 28 de mar\\u00e7o.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">A concession\\u00e1ria programou as interven\\u00e7\\u00f5es para os fins de semana para n\\u00e3o alterar a rotina dos dias de maior movimento de passageiros no metr\\u00f4.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">Em caso de d\\u00favidas, entre em contato com a Central de Atendimento da CCR Metr\\u00f4 Bahia pelo 0800 071-8020.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><em><strong>Fonte: CCR Metr\\u00f4 Bahia<\\/strong><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"40","created":"2015-03-20 16:13:55","created_by":"303","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2015-03-26 20:20:15","modified_by":"303","checked_out":"303","checked_out_time":"2015-03-26 20:20:07","publish_up":"2015-03-20 16:13:55","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":4,"ordering":"0","metakey":"","metadesc":"","access":"1","hits":"1","metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0),
(366, 75, 1, '', '2015-03-26 20:20:29', 303, 10779, '7e619ef9df23318616b59accfcd69b5c6b6313e1', '{"id":75,"asset_id":"256","title":"Comiss\\u00e3o de Desenvolvimento Urbano da AL-BA visita obras do metr\\u00f4 de Salvador","alias":"comissao-de-desenvolvimento-urbano-da-al-ba-visita-obras-do-metro-de-salvador","introtext":"<h5 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">{loadposition position-10}<\\/h5>\\r\\n<h1 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px; text-align: justify;\\">Comiss\\u00e3o de Desenvolvimento Urbano da AL-BA visita obras do metr\\u00f4 de Salvador<\\/h1>\\r\\n<h5 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\"><em>Salvador, 26 de Mar\\u00e7o de 2015<\\/em><\\/h5>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 12.1599998474121px; line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<div id=\\"attachment_19756\\" class=\\"wp-caption aligncenter\\" style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px auto 20px; padding: 4px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; line-height: 18px; text-align: center; color: #666666; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; width: 586px; max-width: 632px !important; background: #f1f1f1;\\"><a style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #0066cc; background: transparent;\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sedur.ba.gov.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2015\\/03\\/DSC_1230.jpg\\"><img class=\\" wp-image-19756 \\" style=\\"border: none; margin: 5px 5px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; opacity: 1; background: transparent;\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sedur.ba.gov.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2015\\/03\\/DSC_1230.jpg\\" alt=\\"Comiss\\u00e3o da AL-BA visitou obras da Linha 1 do metr\\u00f4\\" width=\\"443\\" height=\\"294\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n<p class=\\"wp-caption-text\\" style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 5px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Arial, Helvetica, ''Nimbus Sans L'', sans-serif; color: #888888; line-height: 19px; background: transparent;\\">Comiss\\u00e3o da AL-BA visitou obras da Linha 1 do metr\\u00f4<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; text-align: justify; background: transparent;\\">A Comiss\\u00e3o Especial de Desenvolvimento Urbano da Assembleia Legislativa da Bahia (AL-BA) visitou, nesta ter\\u00e7a-feira (25), as esta\\u00e7\\u00f5es Acesso Norte e Retiro do Metr\\u00f4 de Salvador, e as obras das esta\\u00e7\\u00f5es Bom Ju\\u00e1 e Piraj\\u00e1. A visita \\u2013 que atendeu a uma solicita\\u00e7\\u00e3o da Comiss\\u00e3o \\u2013 foi acompanhada pelo secret\\u00e1rio de Desenvolvimento Urbano da Bahia, Carlos Martins e pelos presidentes da CTB, Eduardo Copello, e da CCR, Luiz Valen\\u00e7a. Entre os deputados presentes na visita estavam, Maria Del Carmen, que tamb\\u00e9m preside a comiss\\u00e3o, Rosemberg Pinto, Vando e Gika Lopes.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; text-align: justify; background: transparent;\\">O grupo visitou primeiramente a esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o Acesso Norte, onde eles conheceram o Centro de Controle Operacional (CCO) e, de l\\u00e1, seguiram de metr\\u00f4 at\\u00e9 a esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o do Retiro, para que os deputados utilizassem o sistema metrovi\\u00e1rio em opera\\u00e7\\u00e3o. \\u201cEssa obra \\u00e9 uma das importantes que ocorre em Salvador nesse momento, porque \\u00e9 a que vai atingir o maior n\\u00famero de popula\\u00e7\\u00e3o e \\u00e9 a maior interven\\u00e7\\u00e3o vi\\u00e1ria. \\u00c9 um sonho dessa cidade ter a quest\\u00e3o do metr\\u00f4 resolvida. E \\u00e9 exatamente por esse simbolismo que n\\u00f3s come\\u00e7amos a realizar estas visitas t\\u00e9cnicas, porque responde a que \\u00e9 poss\\u00edvel ser diferente, quando se tem um projeto adequado, com as solu\\u00e7\\u00f5es adequadas, e \\u00e9 isso que foi mostrado hoje para a Comiss\\u00e3o\\u201d, elogiou a Deputada Del Carmen.<\\/p>\\r\\n<div id=\\"attachment_19757\\" class=\\"wp-caption aligncenter\\" style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px auto 20px; padding: 4px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; line-height: 18px; text-align: center; color: #666666; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; width: 586px; max-width: 632px !important; background: #f1f1f1;\\"><a style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #0066cc; background: transparent;\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sedur.ba.gov.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2015\\/03\\/DSC_1311.jpg\\"><img class=\\" wp-image-19757 \\" style=\\"border: none; margin: 5px 5px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sedur.ba.gov.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2015\\/03\\/DSC_1311.jpg\\" alt=\\"Presidente da CTB, Eduardo Copello apresenta planta do projeto metrovi\\u00e1rio de Salvador\\" width=\\"452\\" height=\\"300\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n<p class=\\"wp-caption-text\\" style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 5px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Arial, Helvetica, ''Nimbus Sans L'', sans-serif; color: #888888; line-height: 19px; background: transparent;\\">Presidente da CTB, Eduardo Copello apresenta planta do projeto metrovi\\u00e1rio de Salvador<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; text-align: justify; background: transparent;\\">O roteiro tamb\\u00e9m incluiu visita \\u00e0 esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o e ao Complexo de Manuten\\u00e7\\u00e3o de Piraj\\u00e1, com previs\\u00e3o de entrega para junho. Durante o percurso at\\u00e9 Piraj\\u00e1, os deputados tiveram a oportunidade de passar pela Esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o Bom Ju\\u00e1, que ser\\u00e1 inaugurada no dia 9 de abril.<br \\/>\\u201cA esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o de Piraj\\u00e1 ser\\u00e1 o c\\u00e9rebro da opera\\u00e7\\u00e3o do sistema metrovi\\u00e1rio, pois dela sair\\u00e1 n\\u00e3o s\\u00f3 o Metr\\u00f4, mas tamb\\u00e9m \\u00f4nibus intermunicipais, interestaduais e futuramente o VLT (Ve\\u00edculo Leve sobre Trilhos)\\u201d, afirmou Copello. De acordo com o presidente da CTB, uma passarela ser\\u00e1 constru\\u00edda para conectar a esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o de transbordo do bairro com a metrovi\\u00e1ria. Mais de quatro mil oper\\u00e1rios trabalham nas obras do metr\\u00f4, sendo que quase metade do efetivo est\\u00e1 somente nas obras de Piraj\\u00e1.<\\/p>\\r\\n<div id=\\"attachment_19758\\" class=\\"wp-caption aligncenter\\" style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px auto 20px; padding: 4px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; line-height: 18px; text-align: center; color: #666666; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; width: 586px; max-width: 632px !important; background: #f1f1f1;\\"><a style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #0066cc; background: transparent;\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sedur.ba.gov.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2015\\/03\\/DSC_1358.jpg\\"><img class=\\" wp-image-19758 \\" style=\\"border: none; margin: 5px 5px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; opacity: 0.981744371203252; background: transparent;\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sedur.ba.gov.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2015\\/03\\/DSC_1358.jpg\\" alt=\\"Obras do complexo e da esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o Piraj\\u00e1. Local vai funcionar como ''c\\u00e9rebro'' do metr\\u00f4 \\" width=\\"576\\" height=\\"278\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n<p class=\\"wp-caption-text\\" style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 5px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Arial, Helvetica, ''Nimbus Sans L'', sans-serif; color: #888888; line-height: 19px; background: transparent;\\">Obras do complexo e da esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o Piraj\\u00e1. Local vai funcionar como \\u2018c\\u00e9rebro\\u2019 do metr\\u00f4<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; text-align: justify; background: transparent;\\">Originalmente a Linha 1 do Metr\\u00f4 terminaria na Esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o Piraj\\u00e1, mas quando a licita\\u00e7\\u00e3o passou para responsabilidade do Governo do Estado foi decidido que haveria uma extens\\u00e3o da Linha 1, com mais duas esta\\u00e7\\u00f5es at\\u00e9 \\u00c1guas Claras. As obras da Linha 2 do Metr\\u00f4 est\\u00e3o acontecendo simultaneamente \\u00e0 finaliza\\u00e7\\u00e3o da esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o Piraj\\u00e1.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; background: transparent;\\"><em style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\\"><strong style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\\">Fonte: Ascom\\/Sedur<\\/strong><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 12.1599998474121px; line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 12.1599998474121px; line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">{loadposition position-4}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 12.1599998474121px; line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">{loadposition position-5}<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"8","created":"2015-03-26 20:14:27","created_by":"303","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2015-03-26 20:20:29","modified_by":"303","checked_out":"303","checked_out_time":"2015-03-26 20:20:22","publish_up":"2015-03-26 20:14:27","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":2,"ordering":"0","metakey":"","metadesc":"","access":"1","hits":"0","metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0),
(367, 75, 1, '', '2015-03-26 20:20:56', 303, 10779, '88b32dd64ef27637cccbdbc6d791cba109f6d61d', '{"id":75,"asset_id":"256","title":"Comiss\\u00e3o de Desenvolvimento Urbano da AL-BA visita obras do metr\\u00f4 de Salvador","alias":"comissao-de-desenvolvimento-urbano-da-al-ba-visita-obras-do-metro-de-salvador","introtext":"<h5 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">{loadposition position-10}<\\/h5>\\r\\n<h1 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px; text-align: justify;\\">Comiss\\u00e3o de Desenvolvimento Urbano da AL-BA visita obras do metr\\u00f4 de Salvador<\\/h1>\\r\\n<h5 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\"><em>Salvador, 26 de Mar\\u00e7o de 2015<\\/em><\\/h5>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 12.1599998474121px; line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<div id=\\"attachment_19756\\" class=\\"wp-caption aligncenter\\" style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px auto 20px; padding: 4px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; line-height: 18px; text-align: center; color: #666666; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; width: 586px; max-width: 632px !important; background: #f1f1f1;\\"><a style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #0066cc; background: transparent;\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sedur.ba.gov.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2015\\/03\\/DSC_1230.jpg\\"><img class=\\" wp-image-19756 \\" style=\\"border: none; margin: 5px 5px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; opacity: 1; background: transparent;\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sedur.ba.gov.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2015\\/03\\/DSC_1230.jpg\\" alt=\\"Comiss\\u00e3o da AL-BA visitou obras da Linha 1 do metr\\u00f4\\" width=\\"375\\" height=\\"249\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n<p class=\\"wp-caption-text\\" style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 5px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Arial, Helvetica, ''Nimbus Sans L'', sans-serif; color: #888888; line-height: 19px; background: transparent;\\">Comiss\\u00e3o da AL-BA visitou obras da Linha 1 do metr\\u00f4<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; text-align: justify; background: transparent;\\">A Comiss\\u00e3o Especial de Desenvolvimento Urbano da Assembleia Legislativa da Bahia (AL-BA) visitou, nesta ter\\u00e7a-feira (25), as esta\\u00e7\\u00f5es Acesso Norte e Retiro do Metr\\u00f4 de Salvador, e as obras das esta\\u00e7\\u00f5es Bom Ju\\u00e1 e Piraj\\u00e1. A visita \\u2013 que atendeu a uma solicita\\u00e7\\u00e3o da Comiss\\u00e3o \\u2013 foi acompanhada pelo secret\\u00e1rio de Desenvolvimento Urbano da Bahia, Carlos Martins e pelos presidentes da CTB, Eduardo Copello, e da CCR, Luiz Valen\\u00e7a. Entre os deputados presentes na visita estavam, Maria Del Carmen, que tamb\\u00e9m preside a comiss\\u00e3o, Rosemberg Pinto, Vando e Gika Lopes.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; text-align: justify; background: transparent;\\">O grupo visitou primeiramente a esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o Acesso Norte, onde eles conheceram o Centro de Controle Operacional (CCO) e, de l\\u00e1, seguiram de metr\\u00f4 at\\u00e9 a esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o do Retiro, para que os deputados utilizassem o sistema metrovi\\u00e1rio em opera\\u00e7\\u00e3o. \\u201cEssa obra \\u00e9 uma das importantes que ocorre em Salvador nesse momento, porque \\u00e9 a que vai atingir o maior n\\u00famero de popula\\u00e7\\u00e3o e \\u00e9 a maior interven\\u00e7\\u00e3o vi\\u00e1ria. \\u00c9 um sonho dessa cidade ter a quest\\u00e3o do metr\\u00f4 resolvida. E \\u00e9 exatamente por esse simbolismo que n\\u00f3s come\\u00e7amos a realizar estas visitas t\\u00e9cnicas, porque responde a que \\u00e9 poss\\u00edvel ser diferente, quando se tem um projeto adequado, com as solu\\u00e7\\u00f5es adequadas, e \\u00e9 isso que foi mostrado hoje para a Comiss\\u00e3o\\u201d, elogiou a Deputada Del Carmen.<\\/p>\\r\\n<div id=\\"attachment_19757\\" class=\\"wp-caption aligncenter\\" style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px auto 20px; padding: 4px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; line-height: 18px; text-align: center; color: #666666; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; width: 586px; max-width: 632px !important; background: #f1f1f1;\\"><a style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #0066cc; background: transparent;\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sedur.ba.gov.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2015\\/03\\/DSC_1311.jpg\\"><img class=\\" wp-image-19757 \\" style=\\"border: none; margin: 5px 5px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sedur.ba.gov.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2015\\/03\\/DSC_1311.jpg\\" alt=\\"Presidente da CTB, Eduardo Copello apresenta planta do projeto metrovi\\u00e1rio de Salvador\\" width=\\"452\\" height=\\"300\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n<p class=\\"wp-caption-text\\" style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 5px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Arial, Helvetica, ''Nimbus Sans L'', sans-serif; color: #888888; line-height: 19px; background: transparent;\\">Presidente da CTB, Eduardo Copello apresenta planta do projeto metrovi\\u00e1rio de Salvador<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; text-align: justify; background: transparent;\\">O roteiro tamb\\u00e9m incluiu visita \\u00e0 esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o e ao Complexo de Manuten\\u00e7\\u00e3o de Piraj\\u00e1, com previs\\u00e3o de entrega para junho. Durante o percurso at\\u00e9 Piraj\\u00e1, os deputados tiveram a oportunidade de passar pela Esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o Bom Ju\\u00e1, que ser\\u00e1 inaugurada no dia 9 de abril.<br \\/>\\u201cA esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o de Piraj\\u00e1 ser\\u00e1 o c\\u00e9rebro da opera\\u00e7\\u00e3o do sistema metrovi\\u00e1rio, pois dela sair\\u00e1 n\\u00e3o s\\u00f3 o Metr\\u00f4, mas tamb\\u00e9m \\u00f4nibus intermunicipais, interestaduais e futuramente o VLT (Ve\\u00edculo Leve sobre Trilhos)\\u201d, afirmou Copello. De acordo com o presidente da CTB, uma passarela ser\\u00e1 constru\\u00edda para conectar a esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o de transbordo do bairro com a metrovi\\u00e1ria. Mais de quatro mil oper\\u00e1rios trabalham nas obras do metr\\u00f4, sendo que quase metade do efetivo est\\u00e1 somente nas obras de Piraj\\u00e1.<\\/p>\\r\\n<div id=\\"attachment_19758\\" class=\\"wp-caption aligncenter\\" style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px auto 20px; padding: 4px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; line-height: 18px; text-align: center; color: #666666; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; width: 586px; max-width: 632px !important; background: #f1f1f1;\\"><a style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #0066cc; background: transparent;\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sedur.ba.gov.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2015\\/03\\/DSC_1358.jpg\\"><img class=\\" wp-image-19758 \\" style=\\"border: none; margin: 5px 5px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; opacity: 0.981744371203252; background: transparent;\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sedur.ba.gov.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2015\\/03\\/DSC_1358.jpg\\" alt=\\"Obras do complexo e da esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o Piraj\\u00e1. Local vai funcionar como ''c\\u00e9rebro'' do metr\\u00f4 \\" width=\\"576\\" height=\\"278\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n<p class=\\"wp-caption-text\\" style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 5px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Arial, Helvetica, ''Nimbus Sans L'', sans-serif; color: #888888; line-height: 19px; background: transparent;\\">Obras do complexo e da esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o Piraj\\u00e1. Local vai funcionar como \\u2018c\\u00e9rebro\\u2019 do metr\\u00f4<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; text-align: justify; background: transparent;\\">Originalmente a Linha 1 do Metr\\u00f4 terminaria na Esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o Piraj\\u00e1, mas quando a licita\\u00e7\\u00e3o passou para responsabilidade do Governo do Estado foi decidido que haveria uma extens\\u00e3o da Linha 1, com mais duas esta\\u00e7\\u00f5es at\\u00e9 \\u00c1guas Claras. As obras da Linha 2 do Metr\\u00f4 est\\u00e3o acontecendo simultaneamente \\u00e0 finaliza\\u00e7\\u00e3o da esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o Piraj\\u00e1.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; background: transparent;\\"><em style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\\"><strong style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\\">Fonte: Ascom\\/Sedur<\\/strong><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 12.1599998474121px; line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 12.1599998474121px; line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">{loadposition position-4}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 12.1599998474121px; line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">{loadposition position-5}<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"8","created":"2015-03-26 20:14:27","created_by":"303","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2015-03-26 20:20:56","modified_by":"303","checked_out":"303","checked_out_time":"2015-03-26 20:20:49","publish_up":"2015-03-26 20:14:27","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":3,"ordering":"0","metakey":"","metadesc":"","access":"1","hits":"0","metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0),
(368, 75, 1, '', '2015-03-26 20:21:38', 303, 10296, '31a58fc506bc64d7f4dfce441a377fcddd7fd0b1', '{"id":75,"asset_id":"256","title":"Comiss\\u00e3o de Desenvolvimento Urbano da AL-BA visita obras do metr\\u00f4 de Salvador","alias":"comissao-de-desenvolvimento-urbano-da-al-ba-visita-obras-do-metro-de-salvador","introtext":"<h5 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">{loadposition position-10}<\\/h5>\\r\\n<h1 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px; text-align: justify;\\">Comiss\\u00e3o de Desenvolvimento Urbano da AL-BA visita obras do metr\\u00f4 de Salvador<\\/h1>\\r\\n<h5 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\"><em>Salvador, 26 de Mar\\u00e7o de 2015<\\/em><\\/h5>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 12.1599998474121px; line-height: 15.8079996109009px; padding-left: 30px;\\">\\u00a0<a style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #0066cc; background: transparent;\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sedur.ba.gov.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2015\\/03\\/DSC_1230.jpg\\"><img class=\\" wp-image-19756 \\" style=\\"border: none; margin: 5px 5px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; opacity: 1; background: transparent;\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sedur.ba.gov.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2015\\/03\\/DSC_1230.jpg\\" alt=\\"Comiss\\u00e3o da AL-BA visitou obras da Linha 1 do metr\\u00f4\\" width=\\"375\\" height=\\"249\\" \\/><\\/a><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 12.1599998474121px; line-height: 15.8079996109009px; padding-left: 30px;\\">Comiss\\u00e3o da AL-BA visitou obras da Linha 1 do metr\\u00f4<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; text-align: justify; background: transparent;\\">A Comiss\\u00e3o Especial de Desenvolvimento Urbano da Assembleia Legislativa da Bahia (AL-BA) visitou, nesta ter\\u00e7a-feira (25), as esta\\u00e7\\u00f5es Acesso Norte e Retiro do Metr\\u00f4 de Salvador, e as obras das esta\\u00e7\\u00f5es Bom Ju\\u00e1 e Piraj\\u00e1. A visita \\u2013 que atendeu a uma solicita\\u00e7\\u00e3o da Comiss\\u00e3o \\u2013 foi acompanhada pelo secret\\u00e1rio de Desenvolvimento Urbano da Bahia, Carlos Martins e pelos presidentes da CTB, Eduardo Copello, e da CCR, Luiz Valen\\u00e7a. Entre os deputados presentes na visita estavam, Maria Del Carmen, que tamb\\u00e9m preside a comiss\\u00e3o, Rosemberg Pinto, Vando e Gika Lopes.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; text-align: justify; background: transparent;\\">O grupo visitou primeiramente a esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o Acesso Norte, onde eles conheceram o Centro de Controle Operacional (CCO) e, de l\\u00e1, seguiram de metr\\u00f4 at\\u00e9 a esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o do Retiro, para que os deputados utilizassem o sistema metrovi\\u00e1rio em opera\\u00e7\\u00e3o. \\u201cEssa obra \\u00e9 uma das importantes que ocorre em Salvador nesse momento, porque \\u00e9 a que vai atingir o maior n\\u00famero de popula\\u00e7\\u00e3o e \\u00e9 a maior interven\\u00e7\\u00e3o vi\\u00e1ria. \\u00c9 um sonho dessa cidade ter a quest\\u00e3o do metr\\u00f4 resolvida. E \\u00e9 exatamente por esse simbolismo que n\\u00f3s come\\u00e7amos a realizar estas visitas t\\u00e9cnicas, porque responde a que \\u00e9 poss\\u00edvel ser diferente, quando se tem um projeto adequado, com as solu\\u00e7\\u00f5es adequadas, e \\u00e9 isso que foi mostrado hoje para a Comiss\\u00e3o\\u201d, elogiou a Deputada Del Carmen.<\\/p>\\r\\n<div id=\\"attachment_19757\\" class=\\"wp-caption aligncenter\\" style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px auto 20px; padding: 4px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; line-height: 18px; text-align: center; color: #666666; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; width: 586px; max-width: 632px !important; background: #f1f1f1;\\"><a style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #0066cc; background: transparent;\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sedur.ba.gov.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2015\\/03\\/DSC_1311.jpg\\"><img class=\\" wp-image-19757 \\" style=\\"border: none; margin: 5px 5px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sedur.ba.gov.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2015\\/03\\/DSC_1311.jpg\\" alt=\\"Presidente da CTB, Eduardo Copello apresenta planta do projeto metrovi\\u00e1rio de Salvador\\" width=\\"452\\" height=\\"300\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n<p class=\\"wp-caption-text\\" style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 5px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Arial, Helvetica, ''Nimbus Sans L'', sans-serif; color: #888888; line-height: 19px; background: transparent;\\">Presidente da CTB, Eduardo Copello apresenta planta do projeto metrovi\\u00e1rio de Salvador<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; text-align: justify; background: transparent;\\">O roteiro tamb\\u00e9m incluiu visita \\u00e0 esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o e ao Complexo de Manuten\\u00e7\\u00e3o de Piraj\\u00e1, com previs\\u00e3o de entrega para junho. Durante o percurso at\\u00e9 Piraj\\u00e1, os deputados tiveram a oportunidade de passar pela Esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o Bom Ju\\u00e1, que ser\\u00e1 inaugurada no dia 9 de abril.<br \\/>\\u201cA esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o de Piraj\\u00e1 ser\\u00e1 o c\\u00e9rebro da opera\\u00e7\\u00e3o do sistema metrovi\\u00e1rio, pois dela sair\\u00e1 n\\u00e3o s\\u00f3 o Metr\\u00f4, mas tamb\\u00e9m \\u00f4nibus intermunicipais, interestaduais e futuramente o VLT (Ve\\u00edculo Leve sobre Trilhos)\\u201d, afirmou Copello. De acordo com o presidente da CTB, uma passarela ser\\u00e1 constru\\u00edda para conectar a esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o de transbordo do bairro com a metrovi\\u00e1ria. Mais de quatro mil oper\\u00e1rios trabalham nas obras do metr\\u00f4, sendo que quase metade do efetivo est\\u00e1 somente nas obras de Piraj\\u00e1.<\\/p>\\r\\n<div id=\\"attachment_19758\\" class=\\"wp-caption aligncenter\\" style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px auto 20px; padding: 4px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; line-height: 18px; text-align: center; color: #666666; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; width: 586px; max-width: 632px !important; background: #f1f1f1;\\"><a style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #0066cc; background: transparent;\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sedur.ba.gov.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2015\\/03\\/DSC_1358.jpg\\"><img class=\\" wp-image-19758 \\" style=\\"border: none; margin: 5px 5px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; opacity: 0.981744371203252; background: transparent;\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sedur.ba.gov.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2015\\/03\\/DSC_1358.jpg\\" alt=\\"Obras do complexo e da esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o Piraj\\u00e1. Local vai funcionar como ''c\\u00e9rebro'' do metr\\u00f4 \\" width=\\"576\\" height=\\"278\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n<p class=\\"wp-caption-text\\" style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 5px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Arial, Helvetica, ''Nimbus Sans L'', sans-serif; color: #888888; line-height: 19px; background: transparent;\\">Obras do complexo e da esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o Piraj\\u00e1. Local vai funcionar como \\u2018c\\u00e9rebro\\u2019 do metr\\u00f4<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; text-align: justify; background: transparent;\\">Originalmente a Linha 1 do Metr\\u00f4 terminaria na Esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o Piraj\\u00e1, mas quando a licita\\u00e7\\u00e3o passou para responsabilidade do Governo do Estado foi decidido que haveria uma extens\\u00e3o da Linha 1, com mais duas esta\\u00e7\\u00f5es at\\u00e9 \\u00c1guas Claras. As obras da Linha 2 do Metr\\u00f4 est\\u00e3o acontecendo simultaneamente \\u00e0 finaliza\\u00e7\\u00e3o da esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o Piraj\\u00e1.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; background: transparent;\\"><em style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\\"><strong style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\\">Fonte: Ascom\\/Sedur<\\/strong><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 12.1599998474121px; line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 12.1599998474121px; line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">{loadposition position-4}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 12.1599998474121px; line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">{loadposition position-5}<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"8","created":"2015-03-26 20:14:27","created_by":"303","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2015-03-26 20:21:38","modified_by":"303","checked_out":"303","checked_out_time":"2015-03-26 20:20:56","publish_up":"2015-03-26 20:14:27","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",