(394, 9, 11, '', '2015-04-23 16:20:23', 303, 751, '40502edb5a7805f4b113ba7a2ed4da66419921d1', '{"id":9,"cid":"0","type":"0","name":"Comprasnet","alias":"comprasnet","imptotal":0,"impmade":"0","clicks":"0","clickurl":"http:\\/\\/www.comprasnet.ba.gov.br\\/","state":"0","catid":"42","description":"","custombannercode":"","sticky":"0","ordering":"8","metakey":"","params":"{\\"imageurl\\":\\"images\\\\\\/banners\\\\\\/banner-184.jpg\\",\\"width\\":\\"\\",\\"height\\":\\"\\",\\"alt\\":\\"\\"}","own_prefix":"0","metakey_prefix":"","purchase_type":"-1","track_clicks":"0","track_impressions":"0","checked_out":"303","checked_out_time":"2015-04-23 16:19:21","publish_up":"","publish_down":"","reset":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","created":"2015-04-23 16:19:21","language":"*","created_by":"0","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2015-04-23 16:20:23","modified_by":"303","version":2}', 0),
(395, 79, 1, '', '2015-04-24 16:28:49', 303, 7261, '81b44cf2d90e4ed7743fc8ffb5c0c7f7ab686713', '{"id":79,"asset_id":263,"title":"Esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o de Bom Ju\\u00e1 \\u00e9 inaugurada e Linha 1 completa 9,7 km de extens\\u00e3o","alias":"estacao-de-bom-jua-e-inaugurada-e-linha-1-completa-9-7-km-de-extensao","introtext":"<h5 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">{loadposition position-10}<\\/h5>\\r\\n<h1 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px; text-align: justify;\\">Esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o de Bom Ju\\u00e1 \\u00e9 inaugurada e Linha 1 completa 9,7 km de extens\\u00e3o<\\/h1>\\r\\n<h5 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\"><em>Salvador, 24\\u00a0<\\/em><em>de Abril de 2015<\\/em><\\/h5>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 19px;\\">Um dia ap\\u00f3s o atingir marca recorde de mais de 44 mil usu\\u00e1rios, o governador Rui Costa inaugurou mais uma etapa do metr\\u00f4 de Salvador. A esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o de Bom Ju\\u00e1 \\u00e9 a sexta da Linha 1, que j\\u00e1 possui 9,7 quil\\u00f4metros de extens\\u00e3o e que, desde o in\\u00edcio da sua opera\\u00e7\\u00e3o, em junho do ano passado, j\\u00e1 transportou mais de 4,5 milh\\u00f5es de passageiros. Atualmente, o metr\\u00f4 funciona em opera\\u00e7\\u00e3o assistida das 8h \\u00e0s 18h. Com in\\u00edcio da opera\\u00e7\\u00e3o comercial, o funcionamento passar\\u00e1 a ser de 5h a 0h. A previs\\u00e3o \\u00e9 que a cobran\\u00e7a da tarifa seja iniciada no segundo semestre<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img src=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sedur.ba.gov.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2015\\/04\\/1429787881Estao_Bom_Jua1-1024x682.jpg\\" alt=\\"1429787881Estao_Bom_Jua1\\" width=\\"453\\" height=\\"302\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 19px;\\">A nova esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o, que possui 5.150 metros quadrados de \\u00e1rea constru\\u00edda, beneficia cerca de 70 mil moradores dos bairros da Fazenda Grande do Retiro, S\\u00e3o Caetano, Calabet\\u00e3o, Mata Escura, Arraial do Retiro, Barreiras e S\\u00e3o Gon\\u00e7alo. O projeto de expans\\u00e3o da Linha 1 prev\\u00ea ainda a chegada do sistema metrovi\\u00e1rio at\\u00e9 as regi\\u00f5es de Piraj\\u00e1, Campinas e Cajazeiras. J\\u00e1 a Linha 2, que est\\u00e1 em constru\\u00e7\\u00e3o, ter\\u00e1 12 esta\\u00e7\\u00f5es e ir\\u00e1 at\\u00e9 Lauro de Freitas. No total, ser\\u00e3o quase 42 quil\\u00f4metros que beneficiar\\u00e3o a popula\\u00e7\\u00e3o baiana, transformando o metr\\u00f4 da capital baiana em um dos maiores do pa\\u00eds.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img src=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sedur.ba.gov.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2015\\/04\\/1429800213IMG_20150423_113805-1024x682.jpg\\" alt=\\"1429800213IMG_20150423_113805\\" width=\\"476\\" height=\\"317\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 19px;\\">Segundo Rui Costa, as obras do metr\\u00f4 prosseguem com investimentos e, at\\u00e9 2017, ser\\u00e3o um importante fator de interliga\\u00e7\\u00e3o com outros modais. \\u201cNo in\\u00edcio do segundo semestre, ser\\u00e1 entregue a esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o de Piraj\\u00e1. Esta obra da Linha 1 do metr\\u00f4 chegar\\u00e1 ainda at\\u00e9 \\u00c1guas Claras\\/Cajazeiras. S\\u00e3o mais cinco quil\\u00f4metros, depois de Piraj\\u00e1. L\\u00e1 construiremos um importante equipamento p\\u00fablico, que interligar\\u00e1 n\\u00e3o apenas o metr\\u00f4, mas tamb\\u00e9m o VLT, al\\u00e9m de \\u00f4nibus interestaduais e intermunicipais\\u201d, afirmou o governador.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img src=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sedur.ba.gov.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2015\\/04\\/DSC_3516.jpg\\" alt=\\"Os moradores da regi\\u00e3o de Bom Ju\\u00e1 j\\u00e1 podem utilizar, a partir desta quinta-feira (23), a esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o do metr\\u00f4\\" width=\\"506\\" height=\\"335\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 19px;\\"><span style=\\"color: #888888; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Arial, Helvetica, ''Nimbus Sans L'', sans-serif; text-align: center; background-color: #f1f1f1;\\">Os moradores da regi\\u00e3o de Bom Ju\\u00e1 j\\u00e1 podem utilizar, a partir desta quinta-feira (23), a esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o do metr\\u00f4<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 19px;\\">A esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o Bom Ju\\u00e1 come\\u00e7ou a funcionar logo ap\\u00f3s a solenidade de inaugura\\u00e7\\u00e3o. O evento contou com a presen\\u00e7a do ministro das Cidades, Gilberto Kassab e do secret\\u00e1rio de Desenvolvimento Urbano, Carlos Martins.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img src=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sedur.ba.gov.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2015\\/04\\/142978788222042015EC_133-1024x682.jpg\\" alt=\\"Esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o do Metr\\u00f4 de Bom Ju\\u00e1 Foto: El\\u00f3i Corr\\u00eaa\\/GOVBA\\" width=\\"539\\" height=\\"359\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; background: transparent;\\"><em style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\\"><strong style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\\">Fonte:\\u00a0SEDUR<\\/strong><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; background: transparent;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 12.1599998474121px; line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">{loadposition position-4}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">{loadposition position-5}<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"8","created":"2015-04-24 16:28:49","created_by":"303","created_by_alias":"","modified":"","modified_by":null,"checked_out":null,"checked_out_time":null,"publish_up":"2015-04-24 16:28:49","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":1,"ordering":null,"metakey":"","metadesc":"","access":"1","hits":null,"metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0),
(396, 78, 1, '', '2015-04-24 16:29:20', 303, 7901, 'a9c05e6f054f0927ecb29d70383cf4221a0c5738', '{"id":78,"asset_id":"261","title":"Nova esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o do metr\\u00f4 de Salvador ser\\u00e1 entregue pelo Governo da Bahia nesta quinta-feira (23)","alias":"nova-estacao-do-metro-de-salvador-sera-entregue-pelo-governo-da-bahia-nesta-quinta-feira-23","introtext":"<h5 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">{loadposition position-10}<\\/h5>\\r\\n<h1 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px; text-align: justify;\\">Nova esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o do metr\\u00f4 de Salvador ser\\u00e1 entregue pelo Governo da Bahia nesta quinta-feira (23)<\\/h1>\\r\\n<h5 style=\\"line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\"><em>Salvador, 23\\u00a0<\\/em><em>de Abril de 2015<\\/em><\\/h5>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; text-align: justify; background: transparent;\\">\\u00a0<a style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #0066cc; line-height: 18px; text-align: center; background: transparent;\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sedur.ba.gov.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2015\\/04\\/1420548888IMG_20150106_091520.jpg\\"><img class=\\"wp-image-20056 \\" style=\\"border: none; margin: 5px 5px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; opacity: 0.992934601998623; background: transparent;\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/www.sedur.ba.gov.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2015\\/04\\/1420548888IMG_20150106_091520-1024x682.jpg\\" alt=\\"1420548888IMG_20150106_091520\\" width=\\"475\\" height=\\"316\\" \\/><\\/a><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; text-align: justify; background: transparent;\\"><em>Esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o de metr\\u00f4 Bom Ju\\u00e1 ser\\u00e1 entregue nesta quinta-feira, 23 | Foto: Mateus Pereira\\/GOVBA<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; text-align: justify; background: transparent;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; text-align: justify; background: transparent;\\"><span style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\\">Mais uma a\\u00e7\\u00e3o de desenvolvimento urbano ser\\u00e1 entregue \\u00e0 popula\\u00e7\\u00e3o soteropolitana pelo governo do Estado. A esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o Bom Ju\\u00e1 de metr\\u00f4 entra em opera\\u00e7\\u00e3o assistida nesta quinta-feira, 23, e vai atender cerca de 100 mil moradores. Com a inaugura\\u00e7\\u00e3o, a Linha 1 do metr\\u00f4 chega a 8,7 quil\\u00f4metros de extens\\u00e3o.\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; text-align: justify; background: transparent;\\"><span style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\\">Bom Ju\\u00e1 possui 155 metros de linha reta com f\\u00e1cil acesso para quem mora nas duas margens da BR-324. O local ainda conta com Sala de Supervis\\u00e3o Operacional (SSO), sistema de combate a inc\\u00eandio, pronto socorro e banheiros p\\u00fablicos, inclusive para portadores de defici\\u00eancia.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; text-align: justify; background: transparent;\\"><span style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\\">Desde que o sistema metrovi\\u00e1rio de Salvador foi transferido para o Governo da Bahia em abril de 2013, a obra do metr\\u00f4 ganhou um ritmo acelerado e pouco mais de um ano depois , em junho de 2014, os trens come\\u00e7aram a rodar em opera\\u00e7\\u00e3o assistida. Desde o per\\u00edodo at\\u00e9 agora, o metr\\u00f4 alcan\\u00e7ou a marca de 4,5 milh\\u00f5es de passageiros transportados. O trecho em opera\\u00e7\\u00e3o da Linha 1 e compreende as esta\\u00e7\\u00f5es Lapa, Campo da P\\u00f3lvora, Brotas, Acesso Norte, Retiro e Bom Ju\\u00e1.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; text-align: justify; background: transparent;\\"><span style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\\">Com investimento de R$ 3,6 bilh\\u00f5es para a conclus\\u00e3o da Linha 1 e implanta\\u00e7\\u00e3o da Linha 2, o metr\\u00f4 chegar\\u00e1 ao Aeroporto Internacional de \\u00a0Salvador, em 2017. Est\\u00e1 previsto ainda o investimento em um novo trecho de Piraj\\u00e1 \\u00e0 \\u00c1guas Claras com extens\\u00e3o de 5,5 quil\\u00f4metros. Com isso, em 2017, a linha completa do metr\\u00f4 ter\\u00e1 41 quil\\u00f4metros.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; text-align: justify; background: transparent;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 12.1599998474121px; line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\">{loadposition position-4}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; text-align: justify; background: transparent;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">{loadposition position-5}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; text-align: justify; background: transparent;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 7px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #000000; line-height: 19px; text-align: justify; background: transparent;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"40","created":"2015-04-23 15:52:17","created_by":"303","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2015-04-24 16:29:20","modified_by":"303","checked_out":"303","checked_out_time":"2015-04-24 16:29:11","publish_up":"2015-04-23 15:52:17","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":3,"ordering":"1","metakey":"","metadesc":"","access":"1","hits":"1","metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0);
